                <h3><span class="rule-number">01</span> FOLLOW DISCORD TOS</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>No illegal shit (seriously, we don't want the server nuked)</li>
                    <li>You must be 13+ (Discord's rule, not ours)</li>
                    <li>No doxxing - posting personal info gets you instant banned</li>
                    <li>No actual threats of violence or illegal activity</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">02</span> DON'T BE <em>ACTUALLY</em> EVIL</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Dark humor? Sure. Actual hate speech targeting people? Nah.</li>
                    <li>Edgy jokes are fine, but straight-up bigotry isn't the vibe</li>
                    <li>There's a difference between being chaotic and being a genuine asshole</li>
                    <li>Read the room - if multiple people say stop, probably stop</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">03</span> NSFW HAS ITS PLACE</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>NSFW content stays in NSFW channels ONLY (if we make them)</li>
                    <li>Don't post it in general or you're getting timed out</li>
                    <li>No illegal content, no exceptions</li>
                    <li>Keep your profile pic/username somewhat appropriate</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">04</span> NO SPAM (Unless It's Funny)</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Don't flood channels with the same message 50 times</li>
                    <li>Copypasta is fine occasionally</li>
                    <li>Don't spam DMs to people - that's annoying</li>
                    <li>Server advertisements = instant ban</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">05</span> DRAMA IS ENTERTAINMENT, NOT A LIFESTYLE</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>We love a good roast session or banter</li>
                    <li>Starting genuine beef or trying to turn the server toxic? Not it</li>
                    <li>Take serious arguments to DMs</li>
                    <li>Don't make the server your therapy session 24/7 (a little is fine, we're human)</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">06</span> STAFF WORD IS FINAL</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>Mods are chill but don't test them</li>
                    <li>If they tell you to chill out, chill out</li>
                    <li>Arguing in public channels = mute</li>
                    <li>You can appeal/question decisions in DMs respectfully</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="rule-item">
                <h3><span class="rule-number">07</span> USE COMMON SENSE</h3>
                <ul>
                    <li>If you have to ask "is this too far?" it probably is</li>
